descriptionHTML:
Do you love tennis?! Then this watch face is for you!

Show your passion for sports with this original tennis watch face.

You can switch between three types of tennis court surfaces (grass, clay and hardcourt). These surfaces are inspired by big tennis tournaments such as: Wimbledon, the French Open (Roland Garros), the Australian Open and the US Open. With the built-in watch menu and the phone menu in the Android Wear companion app you can easily switch between your favorite type of tennis surface!

The hour and minute hands are tennis rackets and the tennis ball circles around the court, acting as the second hand.

Features:

- Watch face for Android Wear Devices (Moto 360, G Watch R, Gear Live, SmartWatch 3, Huawei Watch, etc.)
- 3 different types of tennis court surfaces (grass, clay and hardcourt)
- Support for both round and square displays
- Ambient mode
- Watch menu
- Phone menu

If you like the app, please leave a good rating!

In case you encounter any issues or have suggestions, email us at support@zappup.nl
